        <mxCell id="sL-AoYWcA3Gx_Lqf9hoo-63" parent="1" style="shape=note2;boundedLbl=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;size=25;verticalAlign=top;align=left;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Potion: heal 100 HP.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;New HP=min(Current HP+Heal Amount, Max HP) &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;PowerStone: T&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;rigger the special skill effect once, but it does not&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;start or change the cooldown timer. In short, free&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;extra use of the skill.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;SmokeBomb:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;When used, Enemy attacks do 0 damage in the &lt;br&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;current turn and the next turn&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
